attributes.description:
This report displays the last successful job & last failed job per host along with the recent job status. The row color indicates the recent job status. The hosts displayed in this report are based on the time range & filters selected at the top of the dashboard. Users can use playbook or template filter to get a host report of a specific use case (AIC, UIDEXT, SRM, etc.).
This report displays only 1 account at a given time. If no account is selected or multiple accounts are selected, it will report the account with the latest job. For best results, use filter to select 1 account & 1 playbook to determine the host status.
This report is resource intensive and hence it is limited to report for only 1 account with max 5000 rows. This report is primarily intended for users with Customer Level access only.
